GENERAL NOTES
===========================================================================


USER AVATARS

- avatar filename hash is created by MD5-ing the string 'user'+{$userID}


JOB AVATARS

- avatar filename hash is created by MD5-ing the string 'job'+{$jobID}


JOB VANITY URL

- job vanity hash is created by MD5-ing the string 'job'+{$jobID} and using the first 6 characters


IMAGE UPLOADS

- image filename hash is created by MD5-ing the string 'image'+{$imageID}


ICAL FILE CREATION

- UID string is created by MD5-ing the string "$eventID . $eventTitle . $eventCreated . '@wddsocial.com'";